PJ protecting from unbiquotous water runoff and sheetwashing. Rock and cyano on 30% of plot protecting the surface. Few pied dead due to drought. 50% of sage dead or with dying parts due to competition, drought and browsing.
OffsiteInfluences: Road 20m from end of 120 line causing gullies that border the plot.
